# Anthropic API key for the in-browser Vasily chat (prototype only).
#
# WARNING: any value placed here is bundled into the client JS at build time
# and visible to anyone who loads the demo URL. Use a development-only key
# with a low spending cap, or proxy through a backend before any public
# deploy. Do not commit a real billable key.
#
# Without this key the chat falls back to the deterministic keyword router.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Talk to the real FastAPI backend instead of the in-browser mock store.
# VITE_BACKEND_MODE=1
# VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:8000

# Demo affordances (ENG-09). Default ON: keeps the role-switcher, the /dev routes
# and the «0000» OTP hint for the pilot demo. Set to 0 for a real production build
# — the dev backdoors are stripped and the returning patient must sign in with a
# real SMS code (requires VITE_BACKEND_MODE=1 + a real OTP provider on the backend).
# VITE_DEMO_MODE=0
